OL,3,CTeen jailed for 'serious act of
OL,4,Cviolence and robbery'
OL,6,FAnthony McAllister, 18, who robbed a
OL,7,Fman after punching him so hard he
OL,8,Ffractured his victim's jaw, cheekbone
OL,9,Fand eye socket has been given an 18
OL,10,Fmonth, immediate prison sentence.
OL,12,FMcAllister, was aged 17 at the time of
OL,13,Fa violent incident which occurred as a
OL,14,Fman was walking back to his Carlisle
OL,15,Fhotel alone at 11:30pm on 3 August
OL,16,Flast year.
OL,18,FCCTV showed the man pausing outside
OL,19,Fthe Walkabout bar, off Botchergate,
OL,20,Fand in conversation with McAllister,
OL,21,Fwho was present with three companions.
