OL,4,Cviolence and robbery'
OL,6,FMcAllister appeared to deliver a
OL,7,Fsingle forceful blow to the man's face
OL,8,Fout of nowhere.
OL,10,F"He immediately goes to the ground,"
OL,11,Fprosecutor Brendan Burke told Carlisle
OL,12,FCrown Court, "whereupon the defendant
OL,13,Fremoves his neck chain and just walks
OL,14,Foff."
OL,16,FThe man woke in his hotel room the
OL,17,Fnext morning with a significant black
OL,18,Feye, swelling and pain.
