OL,4,Cviolence and robbery'
OL,6,FHe claims he remembered little of the
OL,7,Fincident but realised his silver chain
OL,8,Fwas missing.
OL,10,FMcAllister was found that night,
OL,11,Fhiding and out of breath in an
OL,12,Falleyway between Bedford and Dowbeck
OL,13,Froads in the city.
OL,15,FHe was later exposed as the robber by
OL,16,Fa detective who saw CCTV stills of the
OL,17,Fincident. "He clearly recognised the
OL,18,Fdefendant because he had seen him in
OL,19,Fearlier court proceedings in the
OL,20,Fpublic gallery," said Mr Burke.
