OL,6,FHis victim, a painter and decorator,
OL,7,Fattended hospital in his home city of
OL,8,FSunderland on 5 August where he was
OL,9,Ffound to have fractures to several
OL,10,Fparts of his face.
OL,12,FHe spoke in an impact statement about
OL,13,Fanxiety, a paranoid feeling of
OL,14,Fpersecution that was about to be
OL,15,Fattacked and his confidence being
OL,16,Fdiminished.
OL,18,F"He has generally lost trust in other
OL,19,Fpeople," said the prosecutor.
