OL,6,FMcAllister from Carlisle, admitted
OL,7,Frobbery and over a video link read a
OL,8,Fletter to the sentencing judge.
OL,10,FThe teen spoke of "a lot going on" in
OL,11,Fhis family life at the time, of mental
OL,12,Fhealth "not in the right place" and
OL,13,Fnot recalling the robbery due to
OL,14,Fintoxication.
OL,16,F"I want to sincerely apologise for my
OL,17,Factions. I know what I have done was
OL,18,Fwrong and should not have happened,"
OL,19,Fhe stated, before saying of the
OL,20,Fvictim. "I hope he can find it in his
OL,21,Fheart to forgive me."
